    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ceremonial weapon comprising a noose or lasso. In Hinduism and Buddhism, a supernatural weapon depicted in iconography and the attribute of certain deities such as Ganesha, Yama, and Varuna.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
